by Anthony Catezone
Assistant Sports EditorSeptember  

The Eastern volleyball team concluded its play in the Penn State Classic Sept PERIOD  a  performance now puts the Panthers at  overall PERIOD



The Panthers saw a heartbreaking loss in a fiveset thriller against Portland      PERIOD Freshman Abby Saalfrank stared as recorded her second tripledouble on the year with  kills  assists and  digs PERIOD Saalfrank was also able to chip in three blocks on defense PERIOD

A fine performance was seen out of sophomore Kelsey Roggemann as well as she notched her careerhigh in kills with  and also recorded a careerhigh . attack PERIOD Junior Reynae Hutchinson was key as she had  kills and  digs marking her twentieth career doubledouble PERIOD

Head coach Kate Prices alma mater and No PERIOD  ranked team in the nation in Penn State downed Eastern in straights sets    to close out the tournament PERIOD Saalfrank led all Panthers in kills with eight and in attack with . she was also able to contribute nine assists in the losing effort PERIOD

The classic began with a similar result as Eastern lost to Duquesne in straight sets    PERIOD Senior Alison Berens led with  kills three shy of her careerhigh PERIOD Berens was efficient on both offensive and defensive sides of the ball as she registered a . attack and four blocks respectively PERIOD

The Panthers will begin conference play in their home opener Sept PERIOD  as they are set to take on Southeast Missouri at  p.m PERIOD in Lantz Arena PERIOD The following day at  p.m PERIOD the Panthers will host TennesseeMartin PERIOD
